────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
RESPONSIBLE USE GUIDELINES
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

This software is provided for defensive security and research purposes.
By using this software, you agree to the following guidelines:

PERMITTED USE
  - Protecting your own LLM-powered applications from prompt injection attacks
  - Security research into LLM vulnerabilities, with appropriate ethical oversight
  - Educational use and learning about AI/LLM security
  - Integration into security tooling for your own organisation
  - Red-teaming your own LLM applications with explicit authorisation

PROHIBITED USE
  - Using the included attack patterns or detection signatures to craft
    injection payloads against LLM systems you do not own or are not
    authorised to test
  - Circumventing safety controls of AI systems operated by third parties
  - Any use that violates the terms of service of AI/LLM providers

DISCLAIMER
  This firewall is a heuristic defence tool. It does not guarantee detection
  of all prompt injection attacks, nor does it guarantee zero false positives.
  All verdicts should be treated as advisory signals, not authoritative
  security decisions.

  The authors and contributors of this software accept no responsibility for
  damages arising from the use or misuse of this tool, including security
  incidents that occur despite its deployment.
